          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              4. Pricing
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              All prices are displayed in euros (â‚¬) and are exclusive of taxes unless otherwise stated. Prices may be subject to change without notice, but we will honor the price at the time your order is placed.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Shipping costs, taxes, and customs duties (if applicable) will be added to the total price and clearly indicated before you confirm your order.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              5. Payment
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Payment must be made in full at the time of order unless otherwise agreed in writing. We accept various payment methods as indicated on our website.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              In case of payment failure, we reserve the right to cancel your order. All payments are processed securely through our payment service providers.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              6. Delivery
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Delivery times are estimates and are not guaranteed. We will make every effort to deliver products within the stated timeframe, but delays may occur due to circumstances beyond our control.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Risk of loss and title to products pass to you upon delivery to the carrier. You are responsible for inspecting products upon delivery and reporting any damage or discrepancies within 48 hours.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              7. Returns and Refunds
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Due to the specialized nature of our products (aircraft parts), returns are subject to our approval and specific conditions. Returns must be requested within 14 days of delivery and products must be in their original condition with all documentation.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Refunds, if approved, will be processed within 30 days of receipt of the returned product. Shipping costs for returns are the responsibility of the customer unless the product is defective or incorrect.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              8. Warranties
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              All products are sold with their certification documents (EASA Form 1 or equivalent). We warrant that products conform to their descriptions and certifications at the time of sale.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our products. Our total liability shall not exceed the purchase price of the product.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              9. Intellectual Property
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, images, and software, is the property of SAS AVIACO FRANCE or its licensors and is protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
