            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              10. Limitation of Liability
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              To the maximum extent permitted by law, SAS AVIACO FRANCE shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits or revenues, whether incurred directly or indirectly, or any loss of data, use, goodwill, or other intangible losses.
